---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { siteConfig } from '../site.config';
---

<BaseLayout title="Methodology & Disclosure" description="VPNVerdict testing methodology and affiliate disclosure.">
  <article class="disclosure">
    <nav class="breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
      <a href="/">Home</a>
      <span class="sep">/</span>
      <span class="current">Methodology</span>
    </nav>

    <header class="page-header">
      <span class="page-label">Transparency</span>
      <h1>How we test.<br/><em>How we earn.</em></h1>
      <div class="header-rule"></div>
    </header>

    <div class="content">
      <section>
        <h2>Affiliate Disclosure</h2>
        <p>{siteConfig.siteName} earns commissions when you click affiliate links to VPN services we review. These relationships fund our independent research at no cost to you.</p>
        <p>Affiliate links are marked for full transparency. When you see a button or styled link to a VPN provider, assume it may be an affiliate link.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Our Testing Process</h2>
        <p>Every VPN on this site has been tested hands-on by our editorial team in real-world scenarios. We evaluate:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Speed performance across multiple server locations</li>
          <li>Security features including DNS leak protection and kill switch reliability</li>
          <li>Streaming platform access and consistency</li>
          <li>Privacy policy analysis and jurisdiction assessment</li>
          <li>User experience and cross-platform compatibility</li>
          <li>Customer support quality and responsiveness</li>
          <li>Value for money and pricing fairness</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2>Editorial Independence</h2>
        <p>VPN providers cannot pay for higher rankings or more favorable reviews. We include both strengths and weaknesses for every service. All recommendations come from our editorial team based on testing, not affiliate potential.</p>
      </section>

      <section class="contact">
        <h2>Questions?</h2>
        <p>Reach us at <a href="mailto:info@vpnverdict.net">info@vpnverdict.net</a></p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .disclosure { max-width: var(--max-width); margin: 0 auto; }

  .breadcrumb {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;
    font-size: 0.8rem; color: var(--ink-400); margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }
  .breadcrumb a { color: var(--ink-500); text-decoration: none; }
  .breadcrumb a:hover { color: var(--ink-950); }
  .sep { color: var(--ink-300); }
  .current { color: var(--ink-400); }

  .page-header { margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl); animation: fadeInUp var(--duration-slow) var(--ease-out) both; }
  .page-label { font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.08em; color: var(--ink-400); }
  .page-header h1 { margin-top: var(--space-sm); margin-bottom: var(--space-md); }
  .page-header h1 em { font-style: italic; color: var(--ink-500); }
  .header-rule { height: 2px; width: 48px; background: var(--ink-950); }

  .content section { margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl); }
  .content h2 { margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: var(--space-md); padding-top: var(--space-xl); border-top: 1px solid var(--ink-100); }
  .content section:first-child h2 { border-top: none; padding-top: 0; }
  .content p { color: var(--ink-700); line-height: 1.75; }
  .content ul { color: var(--ink-700); }
  .content li { line-height: 1.75; }
  .contact a { font-weight: 600; text-decoration: underline; text-underline-offset: 3px; }
</style>
